msgid "aRts"
msgstr "aRts"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The sound framework in &kde; 2 and 3. Its single-tasking nature caused "
"problems when two sources of sound were encountered. In the &plasma; desktop "
"it is replaced by Phonon.&newpara; More info:&newpara; &linkstart;\"https://"
"en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ARts\"&linkmid; Wikipedia: ARts&linkend;"
msgstr ""
"&kde इत्यत्र ध्वनिरूपरेखा; 2 and 3. अस्य एककार्यस्वभावः शब्दस्रोतद्वयस्य सम्मुखे समस्यां "
"जनयति स्म । इत्यत्र &प्लाज्मा; डेस्कटॉप् तस्य स्थाने Phonon.&newpara; अधिकविवरणम्:"
"&newpara; &linkstart;\"https://hi.wikipedia.org/wiki/arts\"&linkmid; "
"विकिपीडिया: कला&linkend;"

