#. Tag: glossterm
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "D-Bus"
msgstr "डी-बस"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"D-Bus or Desktop Bus is an inter-service messaging system. Developed by "
"&RedHat;, it was heavily influenced by &kde; 3 DCOP, which it supersedes. "
"Most POSIX operating systems support D-Bus, and a port for Windows exists. "
"It is used by Qt 4 and GNOME.&newpara; More info:&newpara; &linkstart;"
"\"https://freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/dbus/\"&linkmid;FreeDesktop.org: "
"What is D-Bus?&linkend;&newpara; &linkstart;\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"D-Bus\"&linkmid;Wikipedia: D-Bus&linkend;"
msgstr ""
"D-Bus अथवा Desktop Bus इति अन्तरसेवासन्देशप्रणाली अस्ति । &RedHat;द्वारा विकसितं, "
"&kde; ३ डीसीओपी, यस्य स्थानान्तरणं करोति । अधिकांशः POSIX ऑपरेटिंग् सिस्टम् D-Bus "
"इत्यस्य समर्थनं करोति, विण्डोज इत्यस्य कृते पोर्ट् अपि अस्ति । अस्य उपयोगः Qt 4 तथा GNOME "
"इत्यनेन भवति ।&newpara; अधिकविवरणम्:&newpara; &linkstart;\"https://freedesktop."
"org/wiki/Software/dbus/\"&linkmid;FreeDesktop.org: डी-बस् किम्?&linkend;"
"&newpara; &linkstart;\"https://hi.wikipedia.org/wiki/D-Bus\"&linkmid;"
"विकिपीडिया: डी-बस&linkend;"

