#. Tag: glossterm
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "DCOP"
msgstr "डीसीओपी"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<acronym>DCOP</acronym>, which stands for Desktop COmmunication Protocol, is "
"a light-weight interprocess and software componentry communication system "
"used in &kde; 3. Replaced with &DBus; in &kde; SC 4.&newpara; More info:"
"&newpara; &linkstart;\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/DCOP\"&linkmid;"
"Wikipedia: DCOP&linkend;"
msgstr ""
"<acronym>DCOP</acronym>, यस्य अर्थः Desktop COmmunication Protocol इति भवति, "
"&kde; 3. &DBus इत्यनेन प्रतिस्थापितम्; इत्यत्र &kde; अनुसूचित जाति 4.&newfor; "
"अधिकविवरणम्:&newpara; &linkstart;\"https://hi.wikipedia.org/wiki/DCOP"
"\"&linkstart;विकिपीडिया:DCOP&linkend;"

