#. Tag: glossterm
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frameworks"
msgstr "रूपरेखाएँ"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kde; Frameworks 5 is the next generation of &kde; libraries, modularized "
"and optimized for easy integration in &Qt; applications. The Frameworks "
"offer a wide variety of commonly needed functionality in mature, peer "
"reviewed and well tested libraries with friendly licensing terms. There are "
"over 70 different Frameworks providing solutions including hardware "
"integration, file format support, additional widgets, plotting functions, "
"spell checking and more. Many of the Frameworks are cross platform and have "
"minimal or no extra dependencies making them easy to build and add to any "
"&Qt; application.&newpara; More info:&newpara; &linkstart;\"https://"
"community.kde.org/Frameworks\"&linkmid;&kde; Community Wiki: "
"Frameworks&linkend;"
msgstr ""
"&kde; Frameworks 5 इति &kde; पुस्तकालयाः, &Qt; अनुप्रयोगाः। रूपरेखाः "
"मैत्रीपूर्णानुज्ञापत्रशर्तैः सह परिपक्वेषु, सहकर्मीसमीक्षितेषु, सुपरीक्षितेषु च पुस्तकालयेषु "
"सामान्यतया आवश्यकानां कार्यक्षमतायाः विस्तृतविविधतां प्रदाति हार्डवेयर-एकीकरणं, सञ्चिका-"
"स्वरूप-समर्थनं, अतिरिक्त-विजेट्, प्लॉटिङ्ग्-कार्यं, वर्तनी-परीक्षणम् इत्यादीनि च समाविष्टानि "
"समाधानं प्रदातुं 70 तः अधिकाः भिन्नाः Frameworks सन्ति अनेकाः Frameworks cross "
"platform भवन्ति तथा च न्यूनतमानि अथवा अतिरिक्तनिर्भरता नास्ति येन तेषां निर्माणं तथा च "
"कस्यापि &Qt; अनुप्रयोग।&newpara; अधिकविवरणम्:&newpara; &linkstart;\"https://"
"समुदाय.kde.org/रूपरेखा\"&linkmid;&kde; समुदाय विकि: रूपरेखा&linkend;"

